&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그때를 생각하면 나는 늘 둥실둥실 떠 있었던 것 같소.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Thinking back to those days, I felt as though I had been afloat all the time then.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그래, 마치 하늘을 날아다니는 듯한 기분으로 생을 견디고 있었지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Yes, I was enduring life with the feeling of flying in the sky.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그랬기에 나는 내게 날개가 있었는지, 반푼이였던 것인지조차 모르고 살았던 것이오.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Thus, I had been living without knowing for certain if I truly had wings or if I was a mere half-wit.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그래서 언제나 분명하지 아니한 것이오.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Thus, it has always remained unclear.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;내가 그날을 후회하는지 감개하는지조차도.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Unsure if I regret that day, or reminisce it fondly.&lt;/color&gt;

